&lt;Mr. Jax FashionsInc> said it agreed to sell 600,000 common shares to PembertonHouston Willoughby Bell Gouinlock Inc and Dominion SecuritiesInc, which the buyers will offer at 13-5/8 dlrs per share toinstitutional investors.    Closing is expected on April 30, subject to completion ofnecessary regulatory filings. Mr. Jax said proceeds will beused for internal growth and potential acquisitions. Reuter&#3;